title: Stunning Community, Close to Everything You Need!
posting_body: ['Listing #2023', 'If you are looking for a beautiful and spacious apartments in a prestigious Leander neighborhood, surrounded by beautiful homes and open spaces, you have found it here!', 'You will love living within easy reach of the things that matter: coffee, school, work, errands, parks, shopping.', 'And when you’re home, you’ll enjoy a gorgeous apartment outfitted with thoughtful details along with an amazing amenity line-up that allows you to live very, very comfortably.', 'CommunityAmenities:', 'Resort-style pool with sun shelf, cabanas, outdoor kitchen & grilling stations', 'Complimentary WiFi in all social zones', 'State-of-the-art fitness studio with Fitness On-Demand Interactive Classes', 'Yoga & Spin Studio', 'Social kitchen, lounge & coffee bar', 'Billiards gaming area', 'Park-like courtyard with multiple grilling & gathering areas', 'Dog spa & off-leash gated dog park', 'Scheduled package delivery service', 'Electric car-charging stations', 'Attached garages', 'Additional storage available', 'Short Distance to the MetroRail Leander Station', 'Apartment Amenities:', 'Beautiful one, two, and three bedroom apartments', 'Large, bright, and open floor plans', 'Pet-friendly', 'Granite countertops with undermount sinks & luxury fixtures', 'Subway tile backsplashes', 'Upgraded stainless-steel appliance package', 'High ceilings', 'Upgraded baths with double vanities & linen closets', 'Front-loading washer & dryer', 'USB charging outlets', 'Private balcony or patio', 'Call today to schedule your free tour!', 'I have access to over 1000 apartment listing in all areas in and around the beautiful Austin, Texas!', 'Should this listing not fit exactly what you are looking for, I am happy to help you find your next home!', 'Matt Davidson - Licensed Agent', 'Dash Apartment Locating', 'Dash Realty', 'show contact info', 'Listing #2023']
